abstract: Women's World Cup Roundup; Japan defeats Australia, 1-0, in semifinals of Women's World Cup soccer tournament; other tournament news noted.
lead_paragraph: Japan ended Australia’s surprising run with a 1-0 victory in Edmonton, while England defeated Canada, 2-1, in Vancouver.

headline.main: Japan and England to Meet in Women’s World Cup Semifinals
